export const GRID_SIZE = 20;
export const CELL_SIZE = 20;
export const DIRECTIONS = {
  ArrowLeft: {
    code: 37,
    movement: -1,
    rotation: 180//This Rotates pacman to go the oppsite direction
  },
  ArrowUp: {
    code: 38,
    movement: -GRID_SIZE,
    rotation: 270
  },
  ArrowRight: {
    code: 39,
    movement: 1,
    rotation: 0
  },
  ArrowDown: {
    code: 40,
    movement: GRID_SIZE,
    rotation: 90
  }
};
